      "title": "Floods in Afghanistan kill 31 people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At least 31 people have been killed and 17 injured in flash floods in central Afghanistan's Parwan province.",
        "Also, more than 100 people have gone missing due to this disaster, Bakhtar News Agency reported.",
        "Floods in August 2020 killed more than 160 people, mainly in Parwan province of Afghanistan."
      ],
